title: About
text: Hello! My name is Maddie Reisbig, and I am a junior sports media & communication and advertising & public relations double major at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln. I currently work in the athletic department as a Marketing and Fan Experience Intern, overseeing soccer and gymnastics. I am building this website for my SPMC 350 class, and I look forward to sharing my work with you!
